keeps me closely involved

00:01:04.190 --> 00:01:06.570
with wonderful Library
of Congress activities,

00:01:06.570 --> 00:01:11.770
such as the National Book Festival,
which we held very successfully,

00:01:11.770 --> 00:01:18.120
much to our surprise, amazement,
and delight on Labor Day, Saturday,

00:01:18.120 --> 00:01:22.410
and you'll be pleased to know,
we don't have a date yet,

00:01:22.410 --> 00:01:26.940
but we pretty much decided, again,
to our surprise and amazement,

00:01:26.940 --> 00:01:30.440
that we're going to stay at the
Convention Center and be there

00:01:30.440 --> 00:01:34.570
to try to move it a little bit
further towards the fall they have

00:01:34.570 --> 00:01:38.050
the Labor Day weekend that we
got stuck with, But in a way,

00:01:38.050 --> 00:01:42.750
it was our own fault, because we
actually felt we wanted to stay

00:01:42.750 --> 00:01:47.180
