00:02:11.050 --> 00:02:14.990
We are going to be joining with the
University of Maryland in a variety

00:02:14.990 --> 00:02:17.150
of cooperative activities.

00:02:17.150 --> 00:02:20.910
The Young Readers Center was
opened under the auspices

00:02:20.910 --> 00:02:23.970
of the Center for the Book in 2009.

00:02:23.970 --> 00:02:26.640
I'm also a historian for
the Library of Congress,

00:02:26.640 --> 00:02:29.430
