was especially significant.

00:02:29.430 --> 00:02:33.980
It was the first time in
our, at the time, the 2000 --

00:02:33.980 --> 00:02:39.820
209 years that we'd opened a space
directly for service to kids.

00:02:39.820 --> 00:02:44.280
For under 16 accompanied
by an adult, it's a place,

00:02:44.280 --> 00:02:47.410
not a reading room,
but a wonderful reading

00:02:47.410 --> 00:02:52.310
and knowledge-creating space, and
it's in the Jefferson Building.

00:02:52.310 --> 00:02:54.300
